##
## Velocity Template for reset password
##
## Velocity context will contain the following properties
## request - HttpServletRequest
## response - HttpServletResponse
## environment - Spring Environment object for property resolution
## custom - arbitrary object injected by deployer
##
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
    	<meta charset="utf-8">
    	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
    	<title>#springMessageText("idp.resetpasswd.title", "Web Login Service") - #springMessageText("idp.userprefs.title.suffix", "Reset your password")</title>
    	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="$request.getContextPath()/css/main.css">    	
    </head>
    <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <header>
          <img src="$request.getContextPath()#springMessage("idp.logo")" alt="#springMessageText("idp.logo.alt-text", "logo")">
          <h1>#springMessageText("idp.resetpasswd.title.success", "You canceled password reset")</h1>
        </header>

          <a href="$request.getContextPath()/profile/resetpasswordinit">Reset Your Password</a>

      </div>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <div class="container container-footer">
          <p class="footer-text">#springMessageText("idp.footer", "Insert your footer text here.")</p>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
    
 	</body>
</html>
